				h2 Version Control

				table.table.table--alternate.table__version-control
					tr
						td
							| Repository Location:
						td https://your.repo.location
					tr
						td
							| View Repo:
						td
							a(href="#") https://your.repo.location
					tr
						td
							| Activity Log:
						td
							a(href="#") View Log

				h2 Hosting
				p No information available

				.well.clearfix
					h3 Websites

					.well__sub
						.well__sub__title__container
							.well__sub__title
								p Description:
						.well__sub__content__container
							.well__sub__content
